--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, robert riley <bustercross365@y...> 
wrote:
> Megatron Revived/ Organics:
>  
> "I most certainly am not joking.  I nearly crashed into him when I 
arrived.  Besides, I have a score to settle with him.  He is here to 
do what he attempted years ago: destroy the Autobot Matrix."
>  
> Organics stepped forward as her step brother brought the pilot 
with him.
> "And Unicron has his minions in full force.  They managed to take 
our brother, a most powerful bounty hunter.  They took him with 
them, up there," she said, a little sad and point up, to Unicron.
> "WHAT?!?" the clone roared, clinching his fists.  
> Organics rushed to calm the Emperor clone, to some avail.
> 
> Kyle Stewart <dewboy30816@y...> wrote:
> Fortuneteller's jaw dropped, "UNICRON!!!!  THAT'S NOT
> EVEN FUNNY!!!!"  She certainly thought Seer or Deus
> would have informed her if the world-eating-world had
> returned.
> 
> OOC:  What is going on with him, give me some details?
> 
> --- robert riley <bustercross365@y...> wrote:
> > Megatron Revived:
> >  
> > The femme shook the clone's hand.  He noted how
> > small her hand was to his, but he wasn't the average
> > transformer, and the thought entertained him enough
> > for a minute grin.
> > "I think it would be best to get to a base.  With
